The buddy brothers, Zenyatta and Mondatta, took the bus that came four hours later.
So they were not in the accident.
What new adventure awaits the buddy brothers?
As they entered the city of Aswan...
The five nasty bad guys are there!
They are talking to each other.
They drank black tea that was poisoned.
So all we have to do is poison them.
My brother, we are invincible together.
With your Stand, a manga that tells the future,
They are as good as dead!
Our cards are the God of Knowledge, Thoth, and the God of Creation, Khnum!
We are the Zenyatta Mondatta brothers!
Episode 27 Khnum's Zenyatta and Thoth's Mondatta
It is definitely at this cafe,
at this table, where they will drink the poisoned black tea.
by my Stand, the God of Knowledge, Thoth, always come true.
Avdol's neck wound did not damage anything vital, fortunately,
so he will probably be released tomorrow.
Sadly, Kakyoin might be out of action for the rest of this trip.
Hey, there are a lot of cafes around here.
Let us get a drink and relax.
I would like some black tea.
We are in Egypt, which is enemy territory.
More enemies are lurking around us than ever before,
and we do not know when they will attack.
We have to be more careful than we have been when it comes to poison.
From now on, only drink from bottles or cans.
We are going to have cola instead.
Oh, and we will take the caps off at the table ourselves.
Also, I want the third, fourth, and fifth colas from the right.
I will not be able to poison them...
No, my brother's manga is always right.
I must believe in my brother!
If I, the big brother, do not make an effort to achieve our destiny,
we will not be able to defeat them!
This cola is not cold at all.
I am not going to pay, you jackass!
Hey, are the colas not cold?
Even if that guy were our enemy,
and if he were really trying to poison us...
How would he know that we would come in here?
This city has all these cafes, and I happened to choose this one.
If there were only one cafe, maybe, but there are plenty.
I am just saying that being careful cannot hurt.
If you are that concerned, then let us change cafes.
We will go to the one across the street.
A spark from a cigarette some jackass left in the road got into the trash!
We will take three black teas after all.
Man, to throw a lit cigarette in the trash...
This world sure has some real jerks in it.
Who the hell brought a dog in here?!
They even had it in their mouths!
What is supposed to happen after this?
B-But the prediction was not wrong.
Just, Thoth can only see the very near future.
This time, we will use the next prediction to kill them for sure!
Big brother Zenyatta and little brother Mondatta were very frustrated.
Zenyatta and Mondatta chased after the three guys and their dog.
While chasing them, although this is not really important,
the brothers passed a man with a very annoying face.
The brothers hated guys who looked like that.
I bet he did something in a past life...
I am so pissed off all of a sudden.
Even though he had done nothing wrong, Zenyatta senselessly punched him!
The man with the annoying face panicked!
He accidentally dropped his wallet, which was full of money.
They continued to chase Joestar and the others.
Joestar and the others got in a car
and headed to the hospital to see Avdol and Kakyoin.
Zenyatta planted a bomb shaped like an orange in their car.
His head was split into two bloody halves, and he was out of the game for good!
M-M-My Stand, Thoth, can only see the immediate future.
But once it prints a prediction, there is no way to change it!
The bomb will detonate three seconds after he sticks his finger in to peel it.
Jotaro said he was going straight to the hospital.
Do not let him get away!
Hey, do not hide in there!
We told you to come out, damn it!
My Stand, Khnum, is a transforming Stand.
I can change my height, weight, and even smell to whatever I want.
I made the hat by transforming my hair!
You said you were going straight to the hospital.
I left something in the car, so I came back for it.
Jotaro, what happened to your school jacket?
That is really not a good look on you.
I took it to the cleaners, and did not have any money.
Then hurry up and get in the car.
The Jotaro that gets his head blown in half
is not the r-real Jotaro, but... No! M-M-M-Me?!
Nah, a-actually, I think I am going to walk...
What the hell are you talking about, Jotaro?
From here, it will be a lot faster to take the car.
I have to get out of this Jotaro disguise as soon as possible.
O-Or I will be the one who gets blown up!
I just have to throw the orange away!
I will just throw the bomb away
and put it back in the car later,
so it can blow up the real Jotaro!
I cannot believe he jumped in while we are moving.
He is got an orange in his mouth!
That might be a nice gift for Kakyoin and Avdol.
You do not usually make noises like that.
I-I was saying there was a cyow over there...
What the hell are you talking about, Polnareff?
Are we at the hospital yet?
Do that special trick of yours.
O-Oh, that is what you meant.
If that is the trick, while it seems dangerous, I can do it!
Do the one where you have five in your mouth at once!
I want to see it again.
What the hell kind of weird talent does Jotaro have?!
They already think I am acting strange.
They will be even more suspicious of me!
Polnareff already looks like he might start to peel the orange bomb at any time!
I am going to do this!
I just got to do this, right?!
People can do anything when their lives are at stake!
Last time, you drank some juice without putting the cigarettes out.
Please make this prediction go away!
Hurry up and take off your transformation!
If you undo the transformation, then the real Jotaro will get blown up!
Jotaro, you are acting really weird today.
I-I just... f-feel a bit under the weather...
K-Knowing them, once they get suspicious, they are going to keep poking at me!
If I undo the transformation, they will beat me half to death,
but if I do not, then I will get killed by the bomb!
I will just use feeling bad as an excuse.
I will say that I have a stomach ache, and have them let me out of the car.
Jotaro, the way you have your hands together...
You have got your left thumb on top!
Does the real Jotaro always put his right thumb on top?!
What am I going to do?!
H-H-H-How am I going to fool them now?
The way you put your hands together proves that you were a woman in a past life!
that since I put my right thumb on top, I was a man in a past life!
I always put my left thumb on top, myself.
Then you were definitely a woman in a past life, Mr. Joestar.
How would you even prove that?
M-My stomach really is starting to hurt...
Being with these two is going to kill me.
I am going to tell them that my stomach hurts...
Jotaro, let us see who can eat a whole orange faster!
I do not think y-y-you should eat that orange.
It is the one Iggy picked up.
It could have been in the gutter.
It is not dirty or bruised.
I will eat this one, and you try with one of those.
My stomach hurts so bad, I cannot stand it!
I will go behind some rock!
I actually got away, God damn it!
I am going to go undo my transformation behind that rock!
An orange that Iggy picked up, huh...
It really could have been in a gutter.
Now I can use my Stand Khnum's powers to undo the transformation.
My Thoth has not lost yet.
I will do it on my own!
I am going to kill them!
They punched me and stole my wallet!
If you beat the shit out of them,
I will make sure you are richly rewarded!
Despite finally deciding that he would do it on his own,
Mondatta did not have time to get revenge.
But do not give up, Mondatta!
That is just how life is.
Well, if it is not Jotaro.
You are way too quick at taking a shit outside!
You got here faster than a car...
And you got your jacket back from the cleaners, too?
What the hell are you two...
I am going to have one.
Now, let us go find out how Avdol and Kakyoin are doing.
The brothers were taken out of the battle together.
The fight had ended without Jotaro and the others
even knowing they had been attacked.
Hey, look, it is a sword.
I want to cut you down now, too.
Come at me with your Anubis Stand.
